    "We observed a similar trend in the independent Münster-3H test set for PLIP and CONCH (Fig. 5e and Supplementary Fig.",
    "Using gradient-attention maps, we gain insight into the reasoning behind each output.",
    "When estimating tumor thickness, HistoGPT correctly focused on the tumor region (Fig. 4c, left).",
    "However, underestimation occurred when the model struggled to find the correct spatial orientation even though it recognized the tumor mass itself (Fig. 4c, right).",
    "This was even more pronounced for HistoGPT-L trained without a position embedder, which worked on higher resolution patches that provided more detailed but less contextual information."
